(1, 'SUPERSTAR MULES', 100, 600, 0, '<div class=\"text-content___1EWJO\" style=\"white-space: pre-line; width: calc(50% - 15px); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px;\">SUPERSTAR MULES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"AdihausDIN Cn\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px;\">HERITAGE SHOES REDESIGNED AS A MODERN SLIP-ON MULE.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22px;\">Reconstructed. Reimagined. Ever since they first stepped out onto the hardwood in the \'70s, adidas Superstar shoes have been synonymous with boundary-breaking attitudes and evolving style. This pair honours that drive for progress with a sleek, slip-on design that keeps you decked out in casual style, without the need to lace up. So go ahead, slide in and head out. It\'s as easy as that.</p></div>', 2, '2021-05-16 02:28:10', '2021-05-16 05:32:12'),
(2, 'STAN SMITH STAR WARS SHOES', 200, 777, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">STAN SMITH STAR WARS SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">CLASSIC SNEAKERS FOR FANS OF YODA FROM STAR WARS™.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Take it from one of the wisest beings in the galaxy: a green future is our best future. These adidas Stan Smith Star Wars Shoes are made with recycled materials as part of adidas\' commitment to help end plastic waste. They still look as crisp and clean as ever, with a Yoda-shaped heel tab in honour of the Jedi Master.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials. 50% of upper is recycled content. No virgin polyester.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 06:26:46', '2021-05-16 06:26:46'),
(3, 'ULTRABOOST 21 PRIMEBLUE SHOES', 250, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ULTRABOOST 21 PRIMEBLUE SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ULTRABOOST 21, SAY HELLO TO INCREDIBLE ENERGY RETURN.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">The definition of best never rests. When we dropped the first adidas Ultraboosts, they were the best running shoes we ever made. With each new update, we raise the bar. Now you get the cushioning you didn\'t know you needed with the energy return you\'ve always wanted. This version features 6% more Boost capsules and a supportive adidas Primeknit+ upper. It gives you an extra push of energy in each step that comes from the Linear Energy Push system, which offers forefoot and midfoot support.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 06:30:05', '2021-05-16 06:30:05'),
(4, 'ULTRABOOST 21 SHOES', 250, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ULTRABOOST 21 SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ENERGY WAS JUST ENERGY UNTIL ENERGY MET ULTRABOOST 21.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Prototype after prototype. Innovation after innovation. Testing after testing. Meet us in the hot pursuit of the pinnacle harmonization of weight, cushioning, and responsiveness. Ultraboost 21. Say hello to incredible energy return.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 07:07:43', '2021-05-16 07:07:43'),
(5, 'ZX 1000 THE SIMPSONS FLAMING MOE SHOES', 200, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ZX 1000 THE SIMPSONS FLAMING MOE SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ADIDAS X THE SIMPSONS™ ZX 1000 SHOES THAT HONOUR THE FLAMING MOE.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">These adidas x The Simpsons ZX 1000 shoes pay homage to a very special beverage. A Flaming Moe jewel decorates the laces, and a flame graphic shines under the bright orange 3-Stripes.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 07:11:55', '2021-05-16 07:11:55'),
(6, 'GEODIVER PRIMEBLUE SHOES', 150, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">GEODIVER PRIMEBLUE SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">SLEEK TRAINERS DESIGNED TO REDUCE MATERIAL WASTE.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Style or planet? No need to pick sides. Lace into the streamlined design of these sporty shoes and join in adidas\' commitment to help end plastic waste. Their minimalist upper is made with recycled materials and a partially recycled EVA midsole that keeps you walking on clouds. Sometimes, less is more.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primeblue, a high-performance recycled material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic. 50% of the upper is textile, 75% of the textile is Primeblue yarn. No virgin polyester.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 07:15:31', '2021-05-16 07:15:31'),
(7, 'NIZZA RF SHOES', 100, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">NIZZA RF SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"AdihausDIN Cn\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">CANVAS KICKS IN BEACH-READY PRINT.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Escape the daily grind in these low-profile adidas Nizza RF Shoes. For those who love the idea of the \'beach\', but would much rather enjoy a 3D simulation or be sitting under an umbrella admiring the view. Featuring a low-cut canvas upper with digitized seaview print and distinctive rubber toe bumper – all you need to catch a heatwave, your way. Exclusively through adidas.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 07:19:50', '2021-05-16 07:21:55'),
(8, 'X9000L3 PRIMEBLUE SHOES', 200, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">X9000L3 PRIMEBLUE SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">RESPONSIVE RUNNING SHOES MADE WITH THE OCEANS IN MIND.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Run to connect with the city. Head out in these adidas running shoes and connect with the earth, too. Made with recycled materials, they\'re a part of adidas\' commitment to help end plastic waste. They ride on a responsive Boost and EVA midsole, giving an energy-returning feel on any terrain.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primeblue, a high-performance recycled material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic. 50% of the upper is textile, 75% of the textile is Primeblue yarn. No virgin polyester.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 07:31:13', '2021-05-16 07:31:13'),
(9, 'CONTINENTAL 80 SHOES', 200, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">CONTINENTAL 80 SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"AdihausDIN Cn\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">\'80S TENNIS TRAINERS FOR EVERYDAY STYLE.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Whether you played sports in high school, snuck out of class or kept your nose buried in the books, these adidas shoes are right up your alley. They\'re a bit preppy, very sporty and full of \'80s nostalgia. In fact, they pair with everything in your closet, so you can slip them on and reinvent yourself every day. Enjoy the soft leather comfort as you do.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 07:35:01', '2021-05-16 07:35:01'),
(10, 'SUPERSTAR PRIMEBLUE SHOES', 130, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">SUPERSTAR PRIMEBLUE SHOES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">SHELL-TOE SHOES INSPIRED BY OUR OCEANS.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Change is everything. It\'s how we grow. How we learn. Stand up for change every time you lace up in these adidas Superstar shoes. This version of the icon shows off a redesigned upper crafted to reduce material waste. As a reminder that we all have a part to play, embroidered details made from upcycled plastic waste decorate the heel.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primeblue, a high-performance recycled material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic. 50% of the upper is textile, 75% of the textile is Primeblue yarn. No virgin polyester.</p>', 2, '2021-05-16 07:42:25', '2021-05-16 07:42:25'),
(11, 'X GHOSTED.3 TURF BOOTS', 140, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">X GHOSTED.3 TURF BOOTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"AdihausDIN Cn\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">LIGHTWEIGHT BOOTS FOR SUPER-FAST PLAY.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">They can\'t stop what they can\'t see. When fast is too slow on the court, pull on X Ghosted. These adidas turf football boots keep you quick with a lightweight mesh upper and a sleek, low-cut silhouette with a signature Clawcollar shape. The sock-like construction has a supportive feel, so you stay strapped in for every sprint. EVA in the midsole makes for a smooth ride.</p>', 1, '2021-05-16 08:04:35', '2021-05-16 08:04:53'),
(12, 'PREDATOR FREAK.4 TURF BOOTS', 120, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">PREDATOR FREAK.4 TURF BOOTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">TURF FOOTBALL BOOTS BUILT FOR CONTROL.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Walls can\'t contain you. Rivals can\'t hold you back. On the court, you\'re in control. Release your full force of nature in Predator Freak. Dominate the game in these adidas turf football boots. The comfortable upper is soft and adaptive. The outsole gives you high-speed control.</p>', 1, '2021-05-16 08:25:28', '2021-05-16 08:25:28'),
(13, 'PREDATOR MUTATOR 20.4 TURF BOOTS', 200, 259, 10, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">PREDATOR MUTATOR 20.4 TURF BOOTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">HIT THE TARGET IN THESE ARTIFICIAL TURF BOOTS.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Your confidence consumes them. Your vision leaves them nowhere to hide. Seize your unfair advantage and take control in these adidas Predator Mutator 20.4 Turf football boots. Texture on the forefoot will help with ball contact. The soft textile upper moulds to your foot\'s shape, keeping you comfortable during lightning-quick play on the court.</p>', 1, '2021-05-16 08:27:10', '2021-05-16 08:27:10'),
(14, 'COPA 20.3 FIRM GROUND BOOTS', 200, 259, 15, '<h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">FOOTBALL BOOTS FOR A BETTER TOUCH ON FIRM GROUND.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">You don\'t need the spotlight. All you need is a moment. A single instant to turn game on into game over. Transform your touch in these adidas Copa 20.3 football boots. Stitching on the soft leather forefoot helps keep the ball close. The adaptive tongue and stretchy mesh quarter lock you in so you look a cut above.</p>', 1, '2021-05-16 08:47:31', '2021-05-16 08:47:31'),
(15, 'NEMEZIZ.3 TURF BOOTS', 150, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">NEMEZIZ.3 TURF BOOTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">SUPPORTIVE BOOTS FOR AGILE PLAY.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">No cage or court can keep you boxed in. Smaller spaces just mean sweeter moves. Pull on Nemeziz for agility on demand. These adidas football boots have a textile upper that gives you the freedom to move. The turf outsole offers high traction for jinks and feints.</p>', 1, '2021-05-16 08:51:29', '2021-05-16 08:51:29'),
