(29, 'ADILETTE CORK SLIDES', 50, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ADILETTE CORK SLIDES</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">THE ICONIC SANDAL IN BEACH-READY PRINT.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">A tropical take on a summer staple. The adidas adilette Slides have been an icon of 3-Stripe style since the 1970s. Sleek and lightweight for curtains-closed sofa sessions or at the beach topping up your tan. Pair with 3-Stripe ankle socks for \'woke up like this\' swag around the supermarket ice-cream aisle too. Exclusively through adidas.</p>', 5, '2021-05-16 09:36:50', '2021-05-16 09:36:50'),
(30, 'EEZAY FLIP-FLOPS', 40, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">EEZAY FLIP-FLOPS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">BEACH-READY SANDALS WITH LIGHTWEIGHT CUSHIONING.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">A classic design for casual comfort. These lightweight flip-flops are ready to slip on at the beach. Packed with extra cushioning, they have a smooth, lightweight feel.</p>', 5, '2021-05-16 09:38:36', '2021-05-16 09:38:36'),
(31, 'FORUM TEE', 70, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">FORUM TEE</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A SOFT COTTON T-SHIRT WITH FRESH GRAPHICS.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Anyway you slice it, the adidas Trefoil has always stood for individuality and self-expression. Pull on this adidas Forum Tee and carry on the tradition. A sliced Trefoil stands out on the front in textured puff-print for a modern interpretation of archival style. After all, change is part of self-expression isn\'t it?\r\n\r\nOur cotton products support sustainable cotton farming. This is part of our ambition to end plastic waste.</p>', 6, '2021-05-16 19:00:47', '2021-05-16 19:00:47'),
(32, 'STRAWBERRY TREFOIL TEE', 70, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">STRAWBERRY TREFOIL TEE</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A T-SHIRT WITH A FRESH TREFOIL LOGO.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">There\'s no mistaking the adidas Trefoil. Even when it looks like a juicy strawberry. Pull on this soft adidas tee for a look that\'s so fresh you can almost smell it.\r\n\r\nOur cotton products support sustainable cotton farming. This is part of our ambition to end plastic waste.</p>', 6, '2021-05-16 19:02:42', '2021-05-16 19:02:42'),
