(34, 'HEAT.RDY 3-STRIPES TANK TOP', 100, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">HEAT.RDY 3-STRIPES TANK TOP</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A TANK TOP MADE FOR OUTDOOR WORKOUTS IN HOT WEATHER.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">The sand is hot, and the sun is high. And you\'ve got a workout to do. This adidas training tank top helps you get through it. HEAT.RDY technology maximises airflow and wicks moisture so you stay cool and dry through all those burpees. Breathable mesh inserts help out, too. The slim cut means the top won\'t get in your way as you move.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with recycled content as part of our ambition to end plastic waste.</p>', 6, '2021-05-16 19:05:50', '2021-05-16 19:05:50'),
