(38, 'PRIMEBLUE FOR THE OCEANS ICONS GRAPHIC TEE', 48, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">PRIMEBLUE FOR THE OCEANS ICONS GRAPHIC TEE</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">GRAPHIC TEE MADE FROM RECYCLED MATERIALS.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Recycle in style. This adidas short sleeve t-shirt sports a large \"Reduce and Reuse\" graphic on the front chest. Bold colours give you a standout look.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primeblue, a high-performance recycled material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic.</p>', 6, '2021-05-16 19:25:25', '2021-05-16 19:25:25'),
(39, 'GRAPHIC ALLOVER PRINT TEE', 110, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">GRAPHIC ALLOVER PRINT TEE</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A CREWNECK T-SHIRT WITH A CAMO PRINT.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Sometimes camo\'s what you wear to stand out, not to hide. With big brushstrokes, this adidas tee puts a painterly spin on the print. Soft cotton jersey serves as the canvas.\r\n\r\nOur cotton products support sustainable cotton farming. This is part of our ambition to end plastic waste.</p>', 6, '2021-05-16 19:32:56', '2021-05-16 19:32:56'),
(40, 'ARSENAL PRE-MATCH JERSEY', 150, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ARSENAL PRE-MATCH JERSEY</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">THE MOISTURE-WICKING JERSEY ARSENAL PLAYERS WEAR WHEN THEY WARM UP.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">After days of preparation at the training ground, those last few sprints and stretches on the pitch add the finishing touch. Arsenal players wear adidas football jerseys like this one when they warm up before kickoff. Soft fabric and moisture-wicking AEROREADY help them focus. A club badge in white stands out against the vibrant design and highlights your pride.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials.</p>', 6, '2021-05-16 19:36:18', '2021-05-16 19:36:18'),
(41, 'TILES 3-STRIPES ALLOVER PRINT SHORTS', 90, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">TILES 3-STRIPES ALLOVER PRINT SHORTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">FRENCH TERRY SHORTS WITH COLOURFUL 3-STRIPES.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Make every day feel like Saturday. These adidas shorts have the sporty look of shorts you\'d wear for a spur-of-the-moment football match paired with all the comfort of the shorts you wear when the joystick is the only thing you plan to move all day. Because it\'s not an either-or situation. It\'s yes and yes.</p>', 7, '2021-05-16 19:40:11', '2021-05-16 19:40:11'),
