(43, 'TILES 3-STRIPES ALLOVER PRINT SHORTS', 80, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">TILES 3-STRIPES ALLOVER PRINT SHORTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">FRENCH TERRY SHORTS WITH COLOURFUL 3-STRIPES.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Make every day feel like Saturday. These adidas shorts have the sporty look of shorts you\'d wear for a spur-of-the-moment football match paired with all the comfort of the shorts you wear when the joystick is the only thing you plan to move all day. Because it\'s not an either-or situation. It\'s yes and yes.</p>', 7, '2021-05-16 19:43:14', '2021-05-16 19:43:14'),
(44, '4KRFT SPORT GRAPHIC SHORTS', 80, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">4KRFT SPORT GRAPHIC SHORTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">GO-TO SHORTS FOR ANY TYPE OF TRAINING SESSION.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Reach for these adidas training shorts on leg day. They give you a full range of motion through your box jumps and lunges. The stretchy fabric absorbs moisture, so you stay dry. The hem is slightly higher in back, so they don\'t bunch up while you squat.</p>', 7, '2021-05-16 19:44:29', '2021-05-16 19:44:29'),
(45, 'MANCHESTER UNITED 20/21 HOME SHORTS', 100, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">MANCHESTER UNITED 20/21 HOME SHORTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">FAN SHORTS STYLED AFTER THE ONES IN THE CLUB\'S HOME KIT.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Pull on the home colours of Manchester United. These adidas football shorts are a streetwear version of the ones the team wears at Old Trafford. They\'re made of soft fabric that keeps you dry, with a woven badge above the hem.</p>', 7, '2021-05-16 19:46:07', '2021-05-16 19:46:07'),
(46, 'AEROREADY ESSENTIALS TAPERED CUFF WOVEN 3-STRIPES PANTS', 100, 518, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">AEROREADY ESSENTIALS TAPERED CUFF WOVEN 3-STRIPES PANTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ATHLETIC-INSPIRED PANTS WITH BREATHABLE EVERYDAY COMFORT.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Casual Fridays at the office, nights out with your friends, off-duty days relaxing at home. When you\'ve got these adidas essential pants, you\'re ready for anything. Classic 3-Stripes meet ribbed cuffs with retro style. Moisture-absorbing AEROREADY provides dry comfort when you start to move.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials.</p>', 8, '2021-05-16 19:48:39', '2021-05-16 19:48:39');
