(47, 'ADICOLOR CLASSICS FIREBIRD PRIMEBLUE TRACK PANTS', 180, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ADICOLOR CLASSICS FIREBIRD PRIMEBLUE TRACK PANTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">FIREBIRD TRACK PANTS THAT MAKE A VINTAGE STYLE MODERN.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Take a fresh look at a classic. The inspiration for these adidas Firebird track pants comes from a vintage Japanese design. They\'re also made with recycled materials. Who knew that upcycled plastic waste could be transformed into your new favourite pants?\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primeblue, a high-performance recycled material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic.</p>', 8, '2021-05-16 19:51:16', '2021-05-16 19:51:16'),
(48, 'R.Y.V. SWEAT PANTS', 200, 259, 50, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">R.Y.V. SWEAT PANTS</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ADIDAS SWEAT PANTS WITH AUTHENTIC STREET STYLE.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Self-expression is about attitude. Doing it your way. Challenging the expected to create something new, something never seen before. Something yours. Self-expression comes in all forms, and the Reveal Your Voice collection celebrates that. Flashes of colourful nylon stand out down the front of these adidas R.Y.V. sweat pants. Sometimes you don\'t have to say anything to make a statement.</p>', 8, '2021-05-16 19:52:54', '2021-05-16 19:52:54'),
