(51, 'MARATHON 3-STRIPES JACKET', 150, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">MARATHON 3-STRIPES JACKET</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">BOLD LINES AND THOUGHTFUL DESIGN COME TOGETHER IN THIS SPORTY JACKET.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">What you wear matters. This adidas running jacket is made from recycled materials, as part of our commitment to end plastic waste. Show off the bold athletic look with pride. You\'re making a difference.</p>', 10, '2021-05-16 21:19:27', '2021-05-16 21:19:27'),
(52, 'ADICOLOR FTO WINDBREAKER', 270, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ADICOLOR FTO WINDBREAKER</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">AN ADIDAS ADICOLOR WINDBREAKER WITH A RETRO VIBE.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Rock that 3-Stripes style. All day every day. Head out in legit looks no matter the weather in this windbreaker. A tricolour design from the wayback machine gives you throwback sporty cred. Wind? Whatever.\r\n\r\nThis windbreaker is made with Primeblue, a high-performance recycled material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic.</p>', 10, '2021-05-16 21:23:04', '2021-05-16 21:23:04'),
(53, 'R.Y.V. WINDBREAKER', 220, 259, 45, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">R.Y.V. WINDBREAKER</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A LIGHTWEIGHT JACKET FOR LAST-MINUTE LAYERING.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Pound the pavement. Spread the word. Use your voice. When you\'ve got a busy day ahead of you, remember to grab this adidas windbreaker so you can keep going in style and comfort.</p>', 10, '2021-05-16 21:24:31', '2021-05-16 21:24:31'),
