(55, 'ADICOLOR WINDBREAKER', 270, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">ADICOLOR WINDBREAKER</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A CASUAL WINDBREAKER WITH CLASSIC STYLE.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">You don\'t need to reinvent the wheel to recreate a classic. Inspired by archival designs rooted in sport, this fresh take on an adidas windbreaker is an easy win. Signature details are reinterpreted in blue, white and red for a style that stands out. Adjust the hood, zip up the jacket and head into your day.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials.</p>', 10, '2021-05-16 21:28:31', '2021-05-16 21:28:31'),
(56, 'LOVE UNITES HOODIE (GENDER NEUTRAL)', 190, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">LOVE UNITES HOODIE (GENDER NEUTRAL)</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A PULLOVER HOODIE THAT\'S PART OF THE ADIDAS PRIDE COLLECTION.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Love unites. This adidas cotton-blend hoodie spreads the message with colourful graphics on the front and back. Slip it on, and celebrate Pride every day of the year.</p>', 9, '2021-05-16 21:31:33', '2021-05-16 21:31:33'),
