(58, 'FOR THE OCEANS PRIMEBLUE LIGHT VEST', 150, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">FOR THE OCEANS PRIMEBLUE LIGHT VEST</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A HOODED VEST MADE FOR WINDY DAYS.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">When it\'s a little too warm for a jacket but too windy for just a t-shirt, this adidas training vest featuring WIND.RDY hits the sweet spot. Woven fabric made with recycled materials is cut for a loose fit that makes it ideal for layering. Flip up the hood and adjust the hem and you\'re ready to go.</p>', 9, '2021-05-17 02:56:50', '2021-05-17 02:56:50'),
(59, 'STAN SMITH HOODIE (GENDER NEUTRAL)', 200, 259, 0, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">STAN SMITH HOODIE (GENDER NEUTRAL)</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A HOODIE WITH A GRAPHIC THAT SAYS IT ALL.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">Clean, green lines salute the legend of a single shoe. The icon? The adidas Stan Smith. Pull on this organic cotton hoodie for a look that speaks for itself. With a style as authentic as you are, you can\'t go wrong.\r\n\r\nThis product is made with organic cotton and is part of our ambition to end plastic waste.</p>', 9, '2021-05-17 02:58:46', '2021-05-17 02:58:46'),
(60, 'CHANGE IS A TEAM SPORT HOODIE', 150, 259, 50, '<h5 class=\"heading___IO3QX\" style=\"font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">CHANGE IS A TEAM SPORT HOODIE</h5><h5 class=\"gl-heading--italic gl-heading--s heading___IO3QX\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;AdihausDIN Cn&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 30px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-line;\">A RETRO SWEATSHIRT FOR PEOPLE WHO AREN\'T AFRAID TO DREAM BIG.</h5><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-line;\">We all have ideas to change the world. But the best ideas, the really big ones? None of us can make them reality on our own. This adidas hoodie reminds us that working together is the real way to change the game.</p>', 9, '2021-05-17 03:00:12', '2021-05-17 03:00:12'),
